{
  "text": "Programs such as Forest Gales (Gardiner et al., 2000) are available to assess specific problems of the vulnerability of trees to wind damage. Other numerical programs are under development to record and model root systems and include their influence in ground models, e.g. [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "96701387"
